messages.messageBody:
>>LOL DH makes awesome lasagna from scratch (even makes the pasta!) -
does that count too?

>If he makes me a pan...I'll count it ;-)

I told DH and he said if you can find your way to our neck of the woods
(east of Hartford CT), he'd gladly make some for you :-) If you can wait
a few months (late spring probably) we should have our grain mill by
then so he can even grind the grains for the flour to make the pasta to
make the lasagna!

Deb
